high_descs: Walk straight then turn right then again turn right and turn left to stand facing the sofa.
Pick up the cellphone from the sofa.
Turn left and walk then turn right to study facing the bowl on the sofa.
Put the cellphone into the bowl lying on the sofa.
Pick up the mobile phone from the bowl.
Turn left and walk after that turn left again and walk then turn left again to stand facing the shelf.
Put the bowl containing mobile phone on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Find the CellPhone and put it into the Bowl then place them on the Shelf

Take the cellphone from the couch.
There is a bowl on the couch.
Put the cellphone into the bowl.
Then take the bowl with phone from the couch.
Turn around and go near the shelf.
Put the bowl with phone on the shelf of the table.
anns.task_desc: Placed the CellPhone with Bowl on the Shelf of the table.

high_descs: Go near to the sofa.
Pick the cellphone from the sofa.
Go near and again turn the bowl.
Put the cellphone into the bowl kept on the table.
Collect the bowl along with the phone.
Turn left to reach the shelf.
Put the bowl along with the phone on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the Bowl along with the CellPhone on the Shelf.
